<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background-color: #22c55e; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 20px; }
      .otp-code { 
        font-size: 36px; 
        font-weight: bold; 
        text-align: center; 
        background-color: #f0fdf4; 
        border: 2px solid #22c55e; 
        padding: 20px; 
        margin: 20px 0; 
        border-radius: 8px; 
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        color: #16a34a;
      }
      .info-box { 
        background-color: #fef3c7; 
        border: 1px solid #f59e0b; 
        padding: 15px; 
        border-radius: 6px; 
        margin: 20px 0; 
      }
      .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #666; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>üéµ Welcome to SoundScape!</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hi <%= @user.name %>!</h2>
        
        <p>Thanks for signing up for SoundScape! To complete your registration and start creating amazing playlists, please enter this verification code in the app:</p>
        
        <div class="otp-code">
          <%= @user.otp_code %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-box">
          <p><strong>‚è∞ Important:</strong> This code will expire in 15 minutes for security reasons.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you didn't create an account with SoundScape, please ignore this email.</p>
        
        <p>Happy listening!<br>üé∂ The SoundScape Team</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>¬© 2025 SoundScape. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>